\id TDX - Paama NT + [pma] -Vanuatu 2015 (DBL 2015)
\h Lis 1
\toc2 Lis 1
\toc1 Lis 1 ten rendemien keil
\mt1 Out keil en Tus Votut koa amul aselus usil rendemien keil enek
\li1 \k Ahi Tamer\k* suval koanik:
\pi2 \xt Mak 10:27; Mak 12:29-30; Luk 1:37; Luk 6:35-36; Sion 4:23-24; Umen 17:22-31; Umen 14:14-17; Rom 1:18-23; Rom 11:33-36; 1Kor 8:4-6; 2Kor 1:3; 1Tim 1:17; 1Tim 6:15-16; Hib 4:13; Hib 10:30-31; Tiem 1:17; 1Pit 1:14-17; 1Sion 1:5; 1Sion 4:7-12,16; Siud 24-25; Rev 4:8-11; Rev 15:3-4\xt*
\li1 \k Iesu Kristo\k*, Natin Ahi, suval koanik:
\li2 Iesu Kristo vi Natin Ahi.
\pi2 \xt Mat 11:27-30; Mat 16:13-17; Luk 1:35; Sion 1:1-18; Sion 5:19-29; Sion 6:35-40; Sion 8:58; Sion 11:25-27; Sion 14:5-11; Sion 17:1-5; Sion 20:26-31; Umen 3:13-16; Umen 4:10-12; Rom 1:3-4; 1Kor 3:11; 2Kor 4:4-6; 2Kor 5:21; Kal 4:4-5; Plp 2:5-11; Kol 1:15-20; Kol 2:9-10; Hib 1:1-14; Hib 7:26-28; 1Sion 2:1-2; 1Sion 5:20; Rev 1:12-18; Rev 19:11-16\xt*
\li2 Natin Ahi mai vi meatin koa avasi.
\pi2 \xt Sion 1:14; Luk 1:26-38; Mat 1:18-25; Luk 2:1-20; Mat 2:1-23; Kal 4:4-5; Plp 2:6-7; Hib 2:14-18\xt*
\li2 Iesu visein meatin keil ka sakin koakeil amesai umai atahos eris.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:23-25; Mat 7:28-29; Mat 9:35-36; Mat 11:1-6; Luk 4:14-44; Umen 10:36-38; Sion 20:30-31;\xt*
\li2 Iesu mumon merikel keil houlu.
\pi2 \xt Mat 8:1-15,23-33; Mat 9:1-7,18-33; Mat 12:9-14,22; Mat 14:15-32; Mat 15:22-28,32-38; Mat 17:14-18; Mat 20:29-34; Mat 21:18-22; Mak 1:21-28; Mak 7:32-37; Mak 8:22-25; Luk 5:4-8; Luk 7:11-15; Luk 13:10-13; Luk 14:1-4; Luk 17:12-14; Luk 22:50-51; Sion 2:1-11; Sion 4:46-54; Sion 5:5-9; Sion 9:1-7; Sion 11:11-44; Sion 21:4-6; Umen 2:22\xt*
\li2 Hetetamen keil avuli kat Iesu ka asan matien mini.
\pi2 \xt Mat 26:47-68; Mat 27:1-2,11-31; Mak 14:43-65; Mak 15:1-20; Luk 22:47-53; Luk 22:63–23:25; Sion 18:1-14,19-24; Sion 18:28–19:16\xt*
\li2 Amuti kat Iesu en aiveave tai ka kei mat eni.
\pi2 \xt Mat 27:32-56; Mak 15:21-41; Luk 23:26-49; Sion 19:17-37\xt*
\li2 Aling teiai onen Iesu en valengeihat tatetahinien tai.
\pi2 \xt Mat 27:57-66; Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Sion 19:38-42\xt*
\li2 Iesu mea ris ran matien ka meatin keil houlu alesi.
\pi2 \xt Mat 28:1-20; Mak 16:1-8; Luk 24:1-49; Sion 20:1–21:14; Umen 1:3-8; Umen 2:24-32; Umen 3:15; Umen 4:10,33; Umen 10:39-43; Umen 13:29-39; Umen 17:2-3,30-31; Rom 1:4; Rom 4:24-25; 1Kor 15:3-8,12-21; Rev 1:18\xt*
\li2 Iesu vina ris en out nesa.
\pi2 \xt Luk 24:50-51; Umen 1:9-11; Umen 2:32-36; Umen 5:30-31; Rom 8:34; Efes 1:20-23; Plp 2:9-11; Hib 1:3-11; Hib 2:9; Hib 4:14-16; Hib 7:25-26; Hib 10:12-14; 1Pit 3:22;\xt*
\li1 \k Ninin Votut\k* suval koanik:
\pi2 \xt Mat 28:19; Mak 1:9-11; Mak 3:28-30; Luk 1:35; Luk 3:16; Luk 4:1; Luk 11:13; Luk 12:12; Sion 1:32-34; Sion 3:5-8; Sion 7:37-39; Sion 14:15-17,26; Sion 15:26; Sion 16:7-15; Sion 20:19-23; Umen 1:4-5,8; Umen 2:1-18,38-39; Umen 4:31; Umen 5:3-5; Umen 8:14-17; Umen 10:44-48; Umen 13:2-4; Umen 15:28; Umen 16:7-10; Umen 19:1-7; Rom 5:5; Rom 7:6; Rom 8:9-16,26-27; 1Kor 2:4,9-16; 1Kor 3:16; 1Kor 6:11,19; 1Kor 12:1-13; 2Kor 1:21-22; 2Kor 5:5; 2Kor 13:13; Kal 3:2-5; Kal 4:6; Kal 5:16-18,22-25; Efes 1:13-14,17; Efes 3:16; Efes 4:3-4,30; Efes 5:18-20; Efes 6:17-18; 1Tes 1:5-6; 1Tes 5:19; 2Tes 2:13; Taet 3:5-6; Hib 2:4; Hib 9:14; 1Pit 1:2,11; 2Pit 1:20-21; 1Sion 2:20; 1Sion 3:24; 1Sion 4:13; 1Sion 5:6-8;\xt*
\li2 Ahi mumoni tounah vasi keil.
\pi2 \xt Mat 19:4; Sion 1:3; Umen 14:15; Umen 17:24-26; Hib 1:2; 1Kor 8:6; Kol 1:15-16; Hib 11:3; Rev 4:11\xt*
\li2 Ahi mul losil kat revi tounah vasi.
\pi2 \xt Mat 6:25-34; Mat 10:29-31; Umen 14:15-17; Rom 8:28; Rom 11:36; Kol 1:17; Hib 1:3; Tiem 4:13-16\xt*
\li1 \k Meatin keil asuval koanik:\k*
\li2 Meatin vasi keil amumon tisaen.
\pi2 \xt Sion 8:7-9; Rom 3:9-20,23; Kal 3:22; Rom 5:12; 1Sion 1:8-10\xt*
\li2 Navong meatin keil amumon tisaen, asuval koanik:
\pi2 \xt Rom 1:18-32; Rom 8:5-8; Kal 5:19-21; Efes 2:1-3; Efes 5:3-5; Kol 3:5-10; Tiem 4:17; 1Pit 4:3; 1Sion 3:4-5\xt*
\li2 Meatin keil koa amul amumon tisaen, mal keke avakur mahien ven.
\pi2 \xt Mat 10:28; Mat 13:41-42; Sion 3:18-20,36; Umen 17:30-31; Rom 1:18-19; Rom 6:23; Kal 6:7-8; Kol 3:5-6; 2Tes 1:7-9; Hib 9:27; Hib 10:26-31; 1Pit 1:17; 1Pit 4:3-5; Siud 7; Rev 20:11-15\xt*
\li1 \k Ahi mul mutut meatin keil ran mahien ten tisaen keil one musil sakien koanik:\k*
\li2 Envatien onen Ahi mul en meatin vasi keil ka en vati voutut moulien one.
\pi2 \xt Sion 3:16; Rom 5:8; 1Tim 2:3-6; 2Pit 3:9; 1Sion 4:9-10\xt*
\li2 Iesu Kristo, Natin Ahi, mat en aiveave vahinat ir.
\pi2 \xt Mak 10:45; Sion 3:16; Rom 4:25; Rom 5:8; 1Kor 15:3-4; 2Kor 5:19-21; 1Pit 1:18-20; Kal 3:13; 1Tim 2:5-6; Hib 2:9; Hib 9:28; 1Pit 2:24-25; 1Pit 3:18; 1Sion 2:2; Rev 5:8-10\xt*
\li2 Navong Iesu mat, ran mue suval sipsip ten sanien votut keke vakas motein meten Ahi ran tisaen keil orer.
\pi2 \xt Mat 26:26-29; Rom 3:25; Rom 5:9-10; Efes 1:7; Hib 9:11-14; 1Sion 1:6-7; Rev 7:14-17;\xt*
\li2 Ka en Iesu Kristo, methos onen Ahi mul en ir.
\pi2 \xt Umen 5:31; Umen 10:43; Umen 26:18; Efes 1:7; Efes 4:32; Kol 1:13-14; Kol 2:13-14; Hib 10:17-18; 1Sion 1:8-10\xt*
\li2 Ka en Iesu Kristo, romai romal en meten Ahi.
\pi2 \xt Umen 13:38-39; Rom 1:16-17; Rom 3:21-26; Rom 5:1,18-19; Kal 2:16; Kal 3:6-9; Taet 3:7;\xt*
\li2 Ahi ling ir en vati moulien tai koa vi heite hau.
\pi2 \xt Sion 3:1-16; Sion 5:19-29; Sion 10:10; Sion 11:25-26; Sion 14:6; Sion 17:2-3; Sion 20:31; Rom 5:21; Rom 6:5-14; Rom 8:10-17; 2Kor 5:17; Kal 2:20; Efes 2:1-6; Kol 2:13; Kol 3:1-4; 2Tim 1:10; Taet 3:4-7; 1Pit 1:23; 1Sion 5:11-13;\xt*
\li2 Ahi sakin ir romai rovi titiali keil onen.
\pi2 \xt Sion 1:12-13; Rom 8:14-17; Kal 4:6-7; Hib 12:5-11; 1Sion 3:1-3\xt*
\li1 \k ?Rehoumon sa navong rokur more longlongien keke Ahi vul lat moulien orer ral min moulien onen Natnali Iesu Kristo? \k*
\li2 Mal keke rehelong hetisa ven tisaen keil orer ka rehehiles ran sakien tisa keil orer.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:17; Mak 6:12; Luk 13:1-5; Luk 15:1-31; Luk 24:45-47; Umen 2:37-40; Umen 3:19-20; Umen 17:29-31; Umen 20:21; Umen 26:19-20; 2Kor 7:8-11; 2Pit 3:9; Rev 9:20-21; 2Kor 7:8-11; 2Pit 3:9\xt*
\li2 Reheling demkatien orer en Iesu keke matien onen mutut ir ran vurohien onen Ahi ven tisaen keil orer.
\pi2 \xt Sion 1:12; Sion 3:15-18,36; Sion 6:47; Sion 14:6; Sion 20:31; Umen 4:12; Umen 16:30-31; Rom 3:20-22; Rom 10:9-10; Kal 2:16; Efes 2:8-9\xt*
\li2 Rehehuli Tus Votut keke rovailea Ahi ka asa koa mal rovoumoni suval titiali keil onen.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:1-4; Mat 5:17-20; Mat 22:29; Sion 8:31-32; Sion 20:31; Umen 20:32; Rom 15:4; Rom 16:26; Kol 3:16; 1Tes 2:13; 1Tim 4:13; 2Tim 3:14-17; Hib 4:12; 1Pit 1:22-25; 2Pit 1:19-21; 2Sion 9-10; Rev 1:3\xt*
\li2 Rehemaen avat keil ten Sios avahi baptaes en ir.
\pi2 \xt Mat 28:18-20; Sion 3:22; Sion 4:1-2; Umen 2:37-42; Umen 8:12,36-38; Umen 10:44-48; Umen 16:14-15,31-33; Umen 19:1-7; Umen 22:12-16; Rom 6:1-4; Kal 3:26-27; Kol 2:12; 1Pit 3:20-22;\xt*
\li2 Rehel rehelah ruai hetal min Kristin sav keil.
\pi2 \xt Mat 18:19-20; Umen 2:41-47; Rom 12:4-8; Efes 1:22-23; Efes 4:11-16; Kol 3:15-17; 1Tim 4:13; Hib 10:24-25\xt*
\li2 Rehel rehekur vituai Anien Votut onen Asuv hetal min Kristin sav keil.
\pi2 \xt Mat 26:26-30; Mak 14:22-26; Luk 22:14-20; 1Kor 10:14-22; 1Kor 11:17-34\xt*
\li1 \k Munak rovi Kristin keil, mal keke rehoumon tounah keil enek: \k*
\li2 Rehelong kat Ahi Tamer ka Iesu Kristo, Asuv orer.
\pi2 \xt Sion 14:15,21,23-24; Sion 15:10-17; Rom 13:8-10; 1Pit 1:14-16; 1Sion 2:3-8; 1Sion 3:22-24; 2Sion 1:5-6;\xt*
\li2 Envatien orer hel en Ahi ka meatin sav keil emun.
\pi2 \xt Mat 22:34-40; Mak 12:28-34; Luk 10:25-37; Sion 14:21; 1Sion 5:3; Mat 5:43-48; Sion 13:34-35; Sion 15:12-17; Rom 12:9-10; Rom 13:8-10; 1Kor 13:1-3; 1Kor 16:14; Kal 5:13-15; 1Tes 4:9-10; 1Pit 1:8; 1Pit 4:8; 1Sion 2:9-11; 1Sion 3:11-18; 1Sion 4:7-21;\xt*
\li2 Reheleisungein sakien keil onen Iesu.
\pi2 \xt Sion 13:34-35; Sion 14:27; Rom 12:9-13; Kal 5:22-26; Kol 3:12-17; 1Tes 5:16-18\xt*
\li2 Rehehis min Ahi.
\li2 Rehehis hemukave?
\pi2 \xt Mat 6:5-13; Mat 7:7-11; Mat 18:19-20; Mak 11:24-25; Luk 11:1-13; Luk 18:1-8; Luk 21:36; Sion 14:13-14; Sion 15:7; Sion 16:23-26; Rom 8:26-27; Rom 12:12; Efes 2:18; Efes 6:18; Plp 4:6-7; Kol 4:2; 1Tes 5:17; 1Tim 2:1-4,8; 1Tim 4:4-5; Hib 4:16; Hib 10:19-22; Tiem 1:5-8; Tiem 4:2-3; Tiem 5:13-18; 1Pit 4:7; 1Sion 3:21-22; 1Sion 5:14-15\xt*
\li2 Koanik sakien keil koa meatin sav keil avis min Ahi eni.
\pi2 \xt Mat 11:25-26; Mat 14:23; Mat 19:13-15; Mak 1:35; Luk 5:16; Luk 6:12; Luk 22:32,39-46; Sion 11:41-42; Sion 17:1-26; Umen 4:24-31; Umen 16:25; Umen 20:36; Umen 21:5; Rom 1:9-10; Rom 10:1-2; Rom 15:30-33; 2Kor 12:7-10; Efes 1:15-20; Efes 3:14-21; Efes 6:19-20; Plp 1:3-5,9-11; Kol 1:9-12; Kol 4:3-4; 1Tes 3:9-13; 2Tes 1:11-12; 2Tes 3:1-5; Hib 5:7; Hib 7:25\xt*
\li2 Rehel rehemasmas Ahi hehi houlu.
\pi2 \xt Luk 17:11-19; Sion 6:11; Rom 1:21; Efes 5:20; Plp 4:4-7; Kol 2:7; Kol 3:17; Kol 4:2; 1Tes 5:18; 1Tim 2:1; 1Tim 4:4-5\xt*
\li2 Rehel rehekataun meatin sav keil.
\pi2 \xt Mat 6:1-4; Mat 7:12; Mat 25:31-46; Luk 3:10-11; Luk 6:38; Umen 11:27-30; 1Kor 10:24; 2Kor 8:1-15; 2Kor 9:1-15; Kal 6:9-10; Plp 4:14-19; Hib 10:24; Hib 13:1-3,16; Tiem 1:27; Tiem 2:15-16; 1Sion 3:16-18;\xt*
\li2 Reheling rendemien orer hel netan.
\pi2 \xt Mat 5:3-12; Mat 18:1-5; Luk 14:7-11; Luk 18:9-14; Efes 4:2; Plp 2:3-11; Kol 3:12-13; Tiem 4:5-10; 1Pit 5:5-7\xt*
\li2 Rehekur rendemien koanik en usite ten mani ka tounah keil orer:
\pi2 \xt Mat 6:19-21,24-34; Luk 12:13-21,32-34; Umen 20:35; 1Tim 6:6-10,17-19; Hib 13:5-6; Tiem 2:1-9; Tiem 5:1-6;\xt*
\li2 Reherpuruntei mesav keil en kot.
\pi2 \xt Mat 5:25-26,38-42; Mat 18:15-17; Rom 12:14-21; 1Kor 6:1-8;\xt*
\li2 Rehehouhou revi min koakeil alosil kat ir.
\pi2 \xt Mat 22:15-22; Umen 5:27-29; Rom 13:1-7; 1Tim 2:1-4; Taet 3:1; 1Pit 2:13-17\xt*
\li2 Reherlingtei tounah tai vahi nesa ramat en moulien orer valin Ahi.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:10; Umen 17:22-31; 1Kor 5:11; 1Kor 6:9-11; 1Kor 8:1-13; 1Kor 10:1-22; 2Kor 6:14-18; Kal 5:19-21; 1Tes 1:9-10; 1Sion 5:21; Rev 21:8; Rev 22:15\xt*
\li2 Rehermumontei sakien ten eimas vuo sakien sav tai vatal min keihoen sav tai koa rokatei ven Ahi.
\pi2 \xt Umen 13:4-12; Umen 19:11-20; Kal 5:19-21; Rev 21:8; Rev 22:15\xt*
\li2 Rehermuastei etai tounah vahi sanien votut vaha min Ahi, vuo ninin tai, vuo meatin tai.
\pi2 \xt Mat 9:13; Mak 12:33; Rom 12:1; Hib 9:6–10:18;\xt*
\li2 Rehermatiltei vatal min meatin tai koa rortetalihetei vatal mini.
\pi2 \xt Mat 5:27-30; Sion 8:2-11; Rom 13:8-10; 1Kor 5:9-11; 1Kor 6:9-20; Kal 5:19; Efes 5:3; Kol 3:5-6; 1Tes 4:1-8; Hib 13:4; Siud 1:7\xt*
\li2 Rehermunmuntei tounah koa kilea vasakin rendemien orer vamai vatisa eni.
\pi2 \xt Rom 13:13; 1Kor 5:11; 1Kor 6:9-11; Kal 5:19-21; Efes 5:18; 1Tim 3:1-3; Taet 1:7; 1Pit 4:3-5\xt*
\li1 \k Sios onen Ahi suval koanik:\k*
\li2 Koakeil avi Sios onen Ahi asuval koanik:
\pi2 \xt Mat 16:13-20; Umen 2:41-42; Rom 12:4-8; 1Kor 12:12-30; Efes 1:22-23; Efes 2:19-22; Efes 4:1-16; Kol 1:18; Hib 10:24-25; 1Pit 2:4-10; Rev 19:5-10\xt*
\li2 Navong roling meatin keil keke avahi hetetamen keil ten Sios, rehetie lat vati meatin keil koa amukonek:
\pi2 \xt Umen 6:1-6; 1Tim 3:1-13; Umen 14:23; Taet 1:5-9;\xt*
\li2 Sakien onen hetetamen keil ten Sios hemukonek:
\pi2 \xt Mat 28:18-20; Luk 22:24-27; Umen 20:17-35; 1Tes 2:1-12; 1Tim 4:1-16; 2Tim 2:1-26; 2Tim 3:10–4:5; Taet 2:7-8; 1Pit 5:1-4\xt*
\li2 Rehehouhou min hetetamen keil orer ten Sios.
\pi2 \xt 1Kor 9:14; Kal 6:6; 1Tes 5:12-13; 1Tim 5:17-22; Hib 13:7,17\xt*
\li1 \k Famle tai hesuval koanik\k*
\li2 Sakien onen koakeil aretalihe hemukonek:
\pi2 \xt Mat 19:4-6; 1Kor 7:1-16; Efes 5:21-33; Kol 3:18-19; Taet 2:3-5; Hib 13:4; 1Pit 3:1-7;\xt*
\li2 Sakien onen titiali keil min tata ka mama keil one hemukonek:
\pi2 \xt Mat 15:3-6; Luk 2:51; Efes 6:1-3; Kol 3:20; 1Tim 5:4,8; Hib 12:7-11\xt*
\li2 Sakien onen tata ka mama keil min titiali keil one hemukonek:
\pi2 \xt Efes 6:4; Kol 3:21; 1Tim 3:4-5\xt*
\li2 Sakien onen vatina keil hemukonek:
\pi2 \xt Umen 6:1; Rom 7:2-3; 1Kor 7:39-40; 1Tim 5:3-16; Tiem 1:27\xt*
\li2 Koakeilu luretetalihe lunatetasiltei ran keilu.
\pi2 \xt Mat 5:31-32; Mat 19:3-9; Luk 16:18; Rom 7:2-3; 1Kor 7:10-16;\xt*
\li1 \k ?Rehoumon sa navong rovisu en avong takeih keil?\k*
\li2 Rehesak mesein ir keke rovahisu en avong takeih keil.
\pi2 \xt Rom 8:18-25,28; 2Kor 1:4; 2Kor 4:16-18; Tiem 1:2-4; 1Pit 1:6-9; 1Pit 5:8-10; 1Pit 2:19-21;\xt*
\li2 Rehesak mesein ir keke rovakur sakpurunien keil ven demkatien orer.
\pi2 \xt Mat 5:10-12; Mak 13:9-13; Luk 12:4-9; Sion 15:18-21; Sion 16:1-4; Umen 5:41; Rom 8:35-37; Rom 12:12-14,17-21; 1Kor 4:11-13; 2Kor 4:8-11; 2Kor 12:10; Plp 1:28-29; 2Tes 1:4-8; 2Tes 3:2-4; 2Tim 3:10-13; Hib 10:32-39; Hib 12:3-4; 1Pit 3:13-17; 1Pit 4:12-19; Rev 2:10\xt*
\li2 Rehermetauntei matien.
\pi2 \xt Sion 6:39-40; Sion 11:17-27; Sion 14:1-4; Rom 8:10-11,38-39; Rom 14:7-9; 1Kor 15:12-58; 2Kor 5:1-10; Plp 1:20-24; 1Tes 4:13-18; Hib 2:14-15; Rev 14:13; Rev 21:1-4; Rev 22:1-5;\xt*
\li2 Ahi ro ven ir ka mul kataun ir.
\pi2 \xt Mat 18:19-20; Mat 28:19-20; Sion 14:16-23; Rom 8:35-39; 2Kor 6:16-18; Efes 3:17-19; Plp 4:13; Kol 2:6-7; 2Tes 3:16; Hib 13:5-6;\xt*
\li2 Temat mul sak visi vapurun ir veni rovi onen Ahi.
\pi2 \xt Mat 13:19; Luk 4:1-13; Luk 22:3-4; Sion 8:42-44; 2Kor 2:10-11; 2Kor 4:4; 2Kor 11:13-15; Efes 2:2; 1Tes 2:18; 2Tes 2:9-12; 1Pit 5:8-9; 1Sion 3:8-10; Rev 12:7-12; Rev 20:1-3,10\xt*
\li2 Ahi mul san keihoen min ir keke rehesesein rendemien onen Temat ka rehehati hekeih en demkatien orer.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:1-11; Mat 6:13; Luk 22:31-32; Sion 17:14-19; Rom 8:31-39; Rom 12:12; Rom 16:19-20; 1Kor 10:12-13; 1Kor 16:13; 2Kor 12:7-10; Efes 3:20-21; Efes 6:10-18; Plp 4:13; 1Tes 3:5-8; 2Tes 3:3; 2Tim 1:7-8; Hib 2:18; Hib 4:14-16; Hib 12:1-2; Tiem 4:7; 1Pit 1:5; 1Pit 5:8-11; 1Sion 4:4; 1Sion 5:3-5; Rev 12:7-12;\xt*
\li2 Avong tei, Ahi mul rali lat meatin keil ran mesaien one.
\pi2 \xt Mat 4:23-25; Mat 9:35; Mat 11:2-5; Umen 3:1-6; Umen 8:4-8; 2Kor 12:7-10; Umen 19:11-16; Umen 28:8-9; 1Kor 12:9,29-30; 1Tim 5:23; 2Tim 4:20; Tiem 5:14-15\xt*
\li1 \k Tounah keil koa Tus Votut mul viteni keke hekistal en avong keil koa hemai.\k*
\li2 Iesu hemai ris en out netan.
\pi2 \xt Mat 24:29-44; Sion 14:1-3; Umen 1:10-11; Umen 3:19-21; Plp 3:20-21; Kol 3:4; 1Tes 1:9-10; 1Tes 3:13; 1Tes 4:13–5:11; 2Tes 1:6-10; 2Tes 2:1-4; 1Tim 6:13-15; 2Tim 4:8; Hib 9:28; 2Pit 3:1-18; 1Sion 3:1-3; Rev 1:7; Rev 22:12-13\xt*
\li2 Ahi helei rahit usite onen meatin vasi keil.
\pi2 \xt Mat 7:21-23; Mat 16:24-27; Mat 25:31-46; Sion 3:18-21; Sion 5:24-29; Umen 17:30-31; Rom 2:1-11; Rom 14:10-12; 1Kor 3:10-15; 1Kor 4:5; Hib 9:27-28; 2Tes 1:5-10; Hib 10:26-31; 1Pit 1:17; 1Pit 4:3-5; 2Kor 5:9-10; Rev 20:11-15\xt*
\li2 Koakeil Ahi voutut moulien one en Iesu Kristo kilea val en out nesa.
